#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/posing/selecting.rst:4
msgid "Selecting"
msgstr "选择"

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/posing/selecting.rst:6
msgid ""
"Selection in *Pose Mode* is very similar to the one in :doc:`Edit Mode </"
"rigging/armatures/bones/selecting>`, with a few specificities:"
msgstr ""
"*姿势模式* 中的选择与文档中的“编辑模式”( :doc:`Edit Mode </rigging/"
"armatures/bones/selecting>` )有一些特点非常相似："

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/posing/selecting.rst:9
msgid "You can only select *whole bones* in *Pose Mode*, not roots/tips..."
msgstr "你只能在 *姿势模式* 中选择 *整个骨骼*，而不是首端/尾端..."

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/posing/selecting.rst:13
msgid "Grouped"
msgstr "Grouped 分组"

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/posing/selecting.rst:15
msgid ""
"You can select bones based on their group and/or layer, through the "
"*Select Grouped* pop-up menu :kbd:`Shift-G`:"
msgstr ""
"你可以通过 *按组选择（Select Grouped）*  弹出菜单来选择基于群组和/或图层"
"的骨骼  :kbd:`Shift-G`:"

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/posing/selecting.rst:17
msgid ""
"To select all bones belonging to the same group(s) as the selected ones, "
"use the *In Same Group* entry :kbd:`Shift-G-Numpad1`."
msgstr ""
"要选择属于与选定的骨骼相同组的所有骨骼，请使用 *群组（In Same Group）* 命"
"令 :kbd:`Shift-G-Numpad1`。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/armatures/posing/selecting.rst:19
msgid ""
"To select all bones belonging to the same layer(s) as the selected ones, "
"use the *In Same Layer* entry :kbd:`Shift-G-Numpad2`."
msgstr ""
"要选择属于与选定的骨骼相同层的所有骨骼，请使用 *层（In Same Layer）* 命"
"令  :kbd:`Shift-G-Numpad2`。"
